<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Password Reset Verification Code</title>
</head>
<body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6;">
    <div style="max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px;">
        <h2 style="color: #333; font-size: 24px;">Password Reset Verification Code</h2>
        <p>Hi <%= fullName %>,</p>
        <p>You are receiving this email because a password reset request was made for your account.</p>
        <div style="background-color: #f8f8f8; padding: 10px; margin-top: 20px;">
            <h2 style="color: #333; font-size: 28px; margin: 0; padding: 0;"><%= resetToken %></h2>
        </div>
        <p>If you did not request a password reset, please disregard this email.</p>
        <p style="margin-top: 20px;">Best regards,<br>ETU POLINEMA Team</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
